ple TV 上观看 IPTV 直播的软件</p>\n<h2>基本介绍</h2>\n<p>五一放假期间分享了我开发的一款 AppleTV 软件 IIVA <a href=\"https://v2ex.com/t/850326#reply79\" rel=\"nofollow\">传送门</a>。</p>\n<p>在各位小伙伴的热心反馈下，历时 6 个多月的打磨，将 IPTV 直播部分切割后单独做了一个软件，现已上架。</p>\n<p>主要功能很简单，即观看 M3U 订阅源，与 iPlayTV 属于同类软件。</p>\n<p>如需反馈，请加飞机群 <a href=\"https://t.me/iivaDev\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://t.me/iivaDev</a></p>\n<h2>下载地址</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/tv/id6443592543\" rel=\"nofollow\">下载安装请点我</a></p>\n<h2>播放界面</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://postimg.cc/ygjQHRR8\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"播放界面\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/gjFf3qk8/1.png\"/></a></p>\n<h2>订阅界面</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://postimg.cc/mcb7G5y7\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"订阅界面\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/rp4j56dZ/Screen-Shot-2022-11-18-at-10-11-43.png\"/></a></p>\n<h2>设置界面</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://postimg.cc/34Npk06R\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"设置界面\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/Ss7GtWfW/Screen-Shot-2022-11-18-at-10-18-48.png\"/></a></p>\n<h2>开屏界面</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://postimg.cc/RJqRxD9g\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"主界面\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/T1JHmzsv/3.png\"/></a></p>\n<p>(声明：本软件不提供任何内容服务，如内置订阅源)</p>\n", "last_modified": 1668740052, "replies": 64, "id": 896152}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9a11/5815/52_large.png?m=1630576655", "name": "hardware", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9a11/5815/52_normal.png?m=1630576655", "title": "硬件", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/hardware", "topics": 4743, "footer": "", "header": "硬件发烧友的讨论节点", "title_alternative": "Hardware", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9a11/5815/52_mini.png?m=1630576655", "stars": 2096, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 52, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 358047, "username": "x97bgt", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/x97bgt", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/470d45256ee34438b017cfb002857fef?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/470d45256ee34438b017cfb002857fef?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/470d45256ee34438b017cfb002857fef?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1540298253, "last_modified": 1643619614}, "last_reply_by": "levelworm", "last_touched": 1668788867, "title": "求教：装机的乐趣在哪里？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/896181", "created": 1668746757, "deleted": 0, "content": "先声明我不玩装机也不打游戏，所以可能比较偏颇。\r\n\r\n我的观点是，只要组装好机器后，就能用个四五年。台式电脑不像手机损耗那么大，系统和应用升级也不频繁，我觉得几年内（即使是游戏迷）也够用。\r\n\r\n那这样，装机的动力在哪里？每每看到 amd 发布新显卡之类的就有好多人跃跃欲试，想着升级到最新的硬件配置。即使有，日常使用不是也感知不到么", "content_rendered": "<p>先声明我不玩装机也不打游戏，所以可能比较偏颇。</p>\n<p>我的观点是，只要组装好机器后，就能用个四五年。台式电脑不像手机损耗那么大，系统和应用升级也不频繁，我觉得几年内（即使是游戏迷）也够用。</p>\n<p>那这样，装机的动力在哪里？每每看到 amd 发布新显卡之类的就有好多人跃跃欲试，想着升级到最新的硬件配置。即使有，日常使用不是也感知不到么</p>\n", "last_modified": 1668753761, "replies": 54, "id": 896181}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 193182, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3621, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 601068, "username": "orenla", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/orenla", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "a